        <section name="DataNucleus db4o sql">
            <p>
                <i>datanucleus-db4o-sql</i> provides support for SQL querying of db4o datastores. It can be used
                outside of a DataNucleus environment, and originated as a GoogleCode project.
                Version 1.0 is for use with JDK1.5 (JDBC 2/3). Version 1.1 is for use with JDK1.6+ (JDBC4).
                <b>In DataNucleus versions 1 and 2 it was called "datanucleus-sql4o"</b>
                <b>This plugin was part of AccessPlatform upto and including 3.0 and is no longer developed</b>
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Compile Requirement : JDK1.5+</li>
                <li>Runtime Requirement : JDK1.5+</li>
                <li>Latest version : 3.0.0.release</li>
                <li>Roadmap : <a href="http://issues.datanucleus.org/browse/SQLFO?report=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.project:roadmap-panel" target="_blank">Via JIRA</a></li>
                <li>License : <a href="../project/license.html">Apache 2</a></li>
                <li>Javadocs : <a href="../javadocs/store.db4o.sql/3.0">3.0</a>, 
                               <a href="../javadocs/sql4o/2.0">2.0</a>, 
                               <a href="../javadocs/sql4o/1.1">1.1</a>, 
                               <a href="../javadocs/sql4o/1.0">1.0</a></li>
                <li>Source : <a href="http://datanucleus.svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/datanucleus/platform/sql4o/trunk/">latest</a></li>
            </ul>

